{
  "stem": "214.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To-- to go to the pharmacies, and go to the dental depots, and make sure that the Nazi owners were removed because they were putting in substitutes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Americans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- they were trying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Americans didn't know what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were no occupation forces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were never doing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- but-- but for me, I-- I got the [? badge. ?] Maybe I still have this ticket, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it occupied my time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was getting lunch there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was paid some, I don't remember how many marks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, I-- when the Joint Distribution Office opened, by then, there were more Jews, and the big-- you know, the big DP camps where [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were hundreds and hundreds coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I went to the Joint, and I offered my services.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, voluntary services.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People needed, you know, translations from Yiddish to Polish, from Yiddish to German, from Polish to German, from German to Polish, God knows.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after the war, I usually, you know, went in there and became quite friendly with the woman who was running it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was-- her name was Flor Levine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, she received-- the Joint Distribution received a letter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I looked at this letter the other day from my mother's cousin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These ones, they are all dead-- that she was overjoyed to hear that-- well, nobody knew me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't know who I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I always was saying, you know, that my mother's-- one of my mother's children remained alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That they were overjoyed to hear, that they would try to bring me to America as soon as-- as they can.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this, I don't know if it's true or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
